most people, Captain.

414
00:12:46,643 --> 00:12:48,077
But she cares what you think.

415
00:12:50,780 --> 00:12:52,715
Fine.
I regret what I said.

416
00:12:52,716 --> 00:12:55,149
But now, I don't know how
to make it right with her.

417
00:12:55,185 --> 00:12:56,552
