452
00:14:01,651 --> 00:14:02,651
You called us useless.

453
00:14:02,652 --> 00:14:04,186
You called us incompetent.

454
00:14:04,187 --> 00:14:05,686
You called us zeros in the sack.

455
00:14:05,722 --> 00:14:06,854
Never happened.

456
00:14:06,890 --> 00:14:09,057
Well, someone said it
to me last night.

457
00:14:09,058 --> 00:14:11,426
Oh, uh, must have been my wife.

458
00:14:11,427 --> 00:14:12,860
How did you solve the case?

459
00:14:12,896 --> 00:14:14,429
We listened to those
voicemails again

460
00:14:14,430 --> 00:14:16,465
