building was covered with these.

465
00:14:26,442 --> 00:14:29,111
Same type of rock that
was thrown through the window.

466
00:14:29,112 --> 00:14:30,212
I can't believe it.

467
00:14:30,213 --> 00:14:31,680
What, you don't think
it could break one?

468
00:14:31,681 --> 00:14:32,680
Watch.

469
00:14:34,784 --> 00:14:36,717
I meant I can't believe
you solved the case.

470
00:14:36,753 --> 00:14:38,152
Well, you were
wrong on that too.

471
00:14:40,957 --> 00:14:44,259
Hi.
My name is Jake Peralta,

472
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:45,726
