488
00:15:17,627 --> 00:15:19,361
"Starts crying"
is a stage direction,

489
00:15:19,362 --> 00:15:20,896
you imbecile!

490
00:15:20,897 --> 00:15:24,066
Also, I fathered two children
with Hoytsman's cleaning lady,

491
00:15:24,067 --> 00:15:25,834
and it was I,
disguised as Geoffrey,

492
00:15:25,835 --> 00:15:28,569
