502
00:15:49,411 --> 00:15:51,712
You really brought
my words to life.

503
00:15:51,713 --> 00:15:53,214
You know, I should write more.

504
00:15:53,215 --> 00:15:54,215
What a rush!

505
00:15:54,216 --> 00:15:56,183
Hoytsman, you don't
have to do this.

506
00:15:56,184 --> 00:15:57,418
Your life's not so bad.

507
00:15:57,419 --> 00:15:59,420
