514
00:16:09,298 --> 00:16:10,298
and no one.

515
00:16:10,299 --> 00:16:11,399
Look, I get it.

516
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:12,867
I know what that feels like.

517
00:16:12,868 --> 00:16:15,703
You've only lived in an ice
cream truck for part of one day!

518
00:16:15,704 --> 00:16:17,305
How could you possibly know?

519
00:16:17,306 --> 00:16:19,440
Well, I know no one's
coming to rescue me.

520
00:16:19,441 --> 00:16:21,742
I was so concerned with saving
myself and my reputation

521
00:16:21,743 --> 00:16:23,076
