522
00:16:24,446 --> 00:16:25,713
Wow.

523
00:16:25,714 --> 00:16:27,782
Sounds like you're
having a breakthrough.

524
00:16:27,783 --> 00:16:29,082
You should act on this.

525
00:16:29,117 --> 00:16:31,619
