597
00:18:52,694 --> 00:18:53,994
I don't know why.

598
00:18:53,995 --> 00:18:56,430
Probably my dad abandoning me.

599
00:18:56,431 --> 00:18:58,766
Maybe something I should work
out in therapy, but...

600
00:18:58,767 --> 00:19:02,403
who has an hour to spare
once every two weeks, right?

601
00:19:02,404 --> 00:19:03,404
Anyways,

602
00:19:03,405 --> 00:19:04,971
I'm sorry I acted
like a jackass.

603
00:19:05,006 --> 00:19:07,274
Wow, Jake, you're so sincere
since you got off coke.

604
00:19:07,275 --> 00:19:09,143
And meth.
That was the hard one to kick.

605
00:19:09,144 --> 00:19:11,345
No, the hard one to kick
is angel dust,

606
00:19:11,346 --> 00:19:13,814
